{"id": "art-1443", "label": "Art. 1443", "title": "Art. 1443", "slug": "art-1443", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_504173354\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2174\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_504173354\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 144<sup>3</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1747882624\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2173\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1747882624\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)Administratorul care are într-o anumit&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span>, direct sau indirect, interese contrare\nintereselor <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> trebuie s&#259; îi <span\nclass=SpellE>în&#351;tiin&#355;eze</span> despre aceasta pe <span class=SpellE>ceilal&#355;i</span>\nadministratori <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> pe cenzori sau auditori\ninterni <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> s&#259; nu ia parte la nicio\ndeliberare privitoare la aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_907743634\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2172\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_907743634\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<span class=SpellE>Aceea&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>obliga&#355;ie</span> o are administratorul în cazul în care,\nîntr-o anumit&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span>, <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;tie</span> c&#259; sunt interesate <span class=SpellE>so&#355;ul</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>so&#355;ia</span> sa, rudele ori afinii s&#259;i\npân&#259; la gradul al IV-lea inclusiv.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1154039725\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2171\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1154039725\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Dac&#259;\nprevederile actului constitutiv nu dispun altfel, <span class=SpellE>interdic&#355;iile</span>\nstabilite la alin. (1) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (2), referitoare la\nparticiparea, la deliberarea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la votul\nadministratorilor, nu sunt aplicabile în cazul în care obiectul votului îl\nconstituie:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1796384084\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2170\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1796384084\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)oferirea spre subscriere, c&#259;tre un administrator sau\nc&#259;tre persoanele <span class=SpellE>men&#355;ionate</span> la alin. (2),\nde <span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iuni</span> sau <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iuni</span>\nale <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_277153416\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2169\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_277153416\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)acordarea de c&#259;tre administrator sau de persoanele <span\nclass=SpellE>men&#355;ionate</span> la alin. (2) a unui împrumut ori\nconstituirea unei <span class=SpellE>garan&#355;ii</span> în favoarea <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_227826925\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i2168\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_227826925\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Administratorul care nu a respectat prevederile alin.\n(1) <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> (2) r&#259;spunde pentru daunele care au\nrezultat pentru societate.</span></p>"}